        <item>
            <title>【评测】Denon PerL Pro 纯白无线蓝牙耳机　AI 度身订做个人最佳 EQ 比例 + 高频有诚意</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/17/denon-perl-pro-white/mobile-music/headphones/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=denon-perl-pro-white</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/17/denon-perl-pro-white/mobile-music/headphones/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 12:15:59 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[音乐耳机]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Denon]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Denon PerL Pro]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[真无线蓝牙耳机]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1243510</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>日本高级音响品牌 Denon 所属的 Sound United 早年被美国医疗科技公司 Masimo 收购，推出新一代高级真无线蓝牙耳机。除了机身设计特别，采用镬型设计外，其更采用了 Masimo 的医学科技，运用 AI 为用家度身订做最佳 EQ 比例。近日更推出了全新纯白色版供用家选择。下面就让小编和大家分享一下 Denon PerL Pro 的听后感吧。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1243567" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09444-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09444-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09444.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1243659" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09514-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09514-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09514.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></span></p><h2></h2><h2>设计质感十足　反光外圈彰显高级地位</h2><p>先从外观说起，Denon PerL Pro 采用磨砂白色机身，可能是为了收纳 10 mm 大单元，耳机外壳比市面上的真无线蓝牙耳机更大。耳机采用圆盘形设计，磨砂白色机身配以反光外圈点缀，质感十足。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1243568" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09447-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09447-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09447.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲PerL Pro 耳机以反光外圈点缀，高级感十足</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1243653" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09491-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09491-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09491.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲或因耳机内有 10 mm 单元， Denon PerL Pro 比一般耳机更大</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1243649" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09474-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09474-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09474.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲充电盒上有 DENON 字样</p><h2>4 款大小耳胶 +记忆耳棉　新增 XS 尺码</h2><p>纯白 Denon PerL Pro 随机附赠「XS、S、M、L」 4 个尺码的耳胶，与先前黑色版本相比增加了「XS」选项，相信是为了照顾耳洞较小的用家。另外亦附有专为运动用家而设的 「Wing Attachment」，以巩固耳机。除此之外 Denon 亦照顾到想进一步提升隔音朋友，随机亦附赠一对记忆耳绵，任君选择。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1243569" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09451-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09451-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09451.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲纯白版本除了加入 XS 耳胶外，亦将 USB-A 接口改为 USB-C，另外随附转接头</p><p>Denon PerL Pro 虽然看起来很「挜拃」，但可能因为其单边重量仅有 8 g，小编实际试戴感受又不太觉得有负担。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1243655" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09494-1-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09494-1-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09494-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲看起来很大，但实际佩戴不会感觉到</p><h2>3 收音咪 + 1 骨传导咪　通话清晰隔绝背景音</h2><p>Denon PerL Pro 耳机每边设有 4 个收音咪，其中一个更为骨传导咪，用家即使在闹市中使用 Denon PerL Pro 通话亦未见有嘈杂声。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1243575" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09456-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09456-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09456.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲耳机背设多个收音 mic</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1243579" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09463-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09463-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09463.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1243578" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09462-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09462-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09462.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>高音嘹亮　适合听女声</h2><p>作为一款高阶真无线蓝牙耳机，Denon PerL Pro 配有 aptX 编码，满足对音质有要求的用家。以下小编就试用 Qualcomm aptX Adaptive 连接 Denon PerL Pro，试听几首歌。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1183478" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Screenshot_20230803-181157-248x580.png" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 248px" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Screenshot_20230803-181157-248x580.png 248w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Screenshot_20230803-181157-385x900.png 385w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Screenshot_20230803-181157.png 685w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Screenshot_20230803-181157-658x1536.png 658w" alt="" width="248" height="580" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲使用 aptX Adaptive 连接</p><p>Denon PerL Pro 女声嘹亮清晰，小编试用这对真无线蓝牙耳机播放房东的猫《你是我最愚蠢的一次浪漫》，女主音的温柔声音犹在耳边，整体听感不会觉得尖锐，反而有一种软绵绵的感觉；背景结他和沙锤伴奏部份亦非常认真，不会马虎了事。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1183488" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Screenshot_20230803-184131-248x580.png" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 248px" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Screenshot_20230803-184131-248x580.png 248w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Screenshot_20230803-184131-385x900.png 385w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Screenshot_20230803-184131.png 685w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Screenshot_20230803-184131-658x1536.png 658w" alt="" width="248" height="580" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲房东的猫《你是我最愚蠢的一次浪漫》</p><p>小编之后亦试听了陈蕾《 娱乐人生》，歌曲节拍感强劲之余亦不会含糊交带女声部分，副歌爆发位更令小编感到惊艳。PerL Pro 高频表现不俗，但低音部分较为失望。幸而使用 Denon Headphone App 以 AI 调校 EQ 后加上其 Immersion Mode 的话，低音下潜力听起来会更强烈。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1183491" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Screenshot_20230803-184053-248x580.png" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 248px" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Screenshot_20230803-184053-248x580.png 248w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Screenshot_20230803-184053-385x900.png 385w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Screenshot_20230803-184053.png 685w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Screenshot_20230803-184053-658x1536.png 658w" alt="" width="248" height="580" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲陈蕾《娱乐人生》</p><h2>医疗级科技收集用家耳蜗结构　AI 度身订做 EQ</h2><p>美国医疗科技公司 Masimo 收购 Denon 后，加入了专利医疗级声学分析技术 「Masimo AAT 自适应声学技术」（Masimo Adaptive Acoustic Technology，AAT）。用家只需下载「Denon Headphones」应用程式，简单注册帐户，之后戴好耳机，AAT 就会自动分析你的内耳结构，并利用 Denon Headphones 专用 App 的 AI 为你度身订做独一无二专属 EQ，提供真正定制的个人化声音。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1243657" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09520-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09520-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09520.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>整个测试非常简单，用家先要找一个安静的地方，再连接耳筒，然后开启「Denon Headphone」应用程式，再按程式的指示照做就行。不过要注意的是，应用程式评估你耳朵内部时会发出尖锐的声音，对高频声音敏感的朋友就要留意一下了。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1182596" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/photo_6213088171747555570_y-268x580.jpg" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/photo_6213088171747555570_y-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/photo_6213088171747555570_y-416x900.jpg 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/photo_6213088171747555570_y.jpg 591w" alt="" width="268" height="580" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1182593" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/photo_6213088171747555571_y-268x580.jpg" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/photo_6213088171747555571_y-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/photo_6213088171747555571_y-416x900.jpg 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/photo_6213088171747555571_y.jpg 591w" alt="" width="268" height="580" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲起始页面</p><p>完成评估后，AI 会为你绘制一个灵敏度频谱图，图中 12 点方向是低频，顺时针方向一直转下去音频就愈高，Denon 的 AI 会为你绘制你专属的耳朵频道，再以 EQ 补足音乐播放效果。蓝色圈圈部分代表标准频谱，粉红色部分就是 Denon AI 侦测出你的听力量频谱。拿小编的灵敏度频谱图作例子，小编在听低中频方面较不灵敏，高频方面则非常敏感。Denon Headphone App 就按照检测结果加强中低频的 EQ，让小编可以听到更多这个频谱的声音。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1183681" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/photo1691153050-268x580.jpeg" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/photo1691153050-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/photo1691153050-416x900.jpeg 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/photo1691153050.jpeg 591w" alt="" width="268" height="580" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲起始页面</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1183682" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/photo1691153050-1-268x580.jpeg" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/photo1691153050-1-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/photo1691153050-1-416x900.jpeg 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/photo1691153050-1.jpeg 591w" alt="" width="268" height="580" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲小编的左右耳评测结果</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1243651" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09478-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09478-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09478.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>总结：女声不含糊　AI EQ 有巧思</h2><p>Denon PerL Pro 整体使用体验不俗，虽然外观看起来有点大，但得益于其 8 g 蝇量级重量，实际佩戴体验不会让用家感受到其存在。音色方面，耳机不负 Denon 之名，所有细节清楚交代之余，女声亦毫不含糊。除此以外，Masimo 带来的「Masimo AAT 自适应声学技术」亦非常有诚意，要试尽耳机的话真的要试玩这个 AI。惟一要弹的就是低频部分，小编觉得要靠 EQ 打救。</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/17/denon-perl-pro-white/mobile-music/headphones/">【评测】Denon PerL Pro 纯白无线蓝牙耳机　AI 度身订做个人最佳 EQ 比例 + 高频有诚意</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
