                <![CDATA[混合实境]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1243532</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">警察机动部队（PTU）总部研究及发展科年初引入混合实境（Mixed Reality）技术，务求加强训练效果。根据《星岛》报道，这个混合实境结合了虚拟实境（VR）与扩增实境（AR）的技术，以感知技术、显示技术、空间映射等科技结合虚拟与真实物件，使受训人员可透过头戴式显示器与虚拟物体和真实环境互动，并在模拟的各种环境中进行战术训练。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1243533" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/1_2-694x463.jpeg" alt="警队「混合实境」技术" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/1_2-694x463.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/1_2.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2005138/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E5%89%8D%E7%B7%9A%E9%83%A8%E9%9A%8A%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97-PTU%E5%BC%95%E5%85%A5-%E6%B7%B7%E5%90%88%E5%AF%A6%E5%A2%83-%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1-%E6%A8%A1%E6%93%AC%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%92%B0%E5%A2%83-%E5%8A%A9%E6%88%B0%E8%A1%93%E8%A8%93%E7%B7%B4%E7%B2%BE%E7%9B%8A%E6%B1%82%E7%B2%BE?fbclid=IwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTAAAR0swAB425v8LCzoXRJExakIBHvPfiSk7Z_bJzmHCDmR8G6VhTQYl_fqalo_aem_rysa03S-sLbDSPxB133l7g">星岛</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1243543 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2_3-694x463.jpeg" alt="警队「混合实境」技术" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2_3-694x463.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2_3.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2005138/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E5%89%8D%E7%B7%9A%E9%83%A8%E9%9A%8A%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97-PTU%E5%BC%95%E5%85%A5-%E6%B7%B7%E5%90%88%E5%AF%A6%E5%A2%83-%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1-%E6%A8%A1%E6%93%AC%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%92%B0%E5%A2%83-%E5%8A%A9%E6%88%B0%E8%A1%93%E8%A8%93%E7%B7%B4%E7%B2%BE%E7%9B%8A%E6%B1%82%E7%B2%BE?fbclid=IwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTAAAR0swAB425v8LCzoXRJExakIBHvPfiSk7Z_bJzmHCDmR8G6VhTQYl_fqalo_aem_rysa03S-sLbDSPxB133l7g">星岛</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1243544 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/7_2-694x463.jpeg" alt="警队「混合实境」技术" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/7_2-694x463.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/7_2.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2005138/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E5%89%8D%E7%B7%9A%E9%83%A8%E9%9A%8A%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97-PTU%E5%BC%95%E5%85%A5-%E6%B7%B7%E5%90%88%E5%AF%A6%E5%A2%83-%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1-%E6%A8%A1%E6%93%AC%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%92%B0%E5%A2%83-%E5%8A%A9%E6%88%B0%E8%A1%93%E8%A8%93%E7%B7%B4%E7%B2%BE%E7%9B%8A%E6%B1%82%E7%B2%BE?fbclid=IwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTAAAR0swAB425v8LCzoXRJExakIBHvPfiSk7Z_bJzmHCDmR8G6VhTQYl_fqalo_aem_rysa03S-sLbDSPxB133l7g">星岛</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">警察机动部队总部研究及发展科总督察郑伟文，解释受训人员所佩戴的开放式头戴显示器装有红外线传感器侦测感知和定位，配备的「模拟枪」同样装有红外线传感器能侦测受训人员的瞄准动作和方向。MR 训练系统安置于地上的「被动式定位方块」将场上人员的定位讯号接收，中央处理系统能实时显示训练情况，受训人员于整个场景的位置、方向，枪的指向等都能展示，并记录于系统中。受训人员以第一人称视角在模拟场景中执行任务，与队友沟通并制定战术，制服匪徒和救出人质。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">MR 训练系统可配合各种需要模拟出不同的场景，训练受训人员于不同情况下的应对能力。凌子杰警司表示整个 MR 训练系统都会精确地记录过程，可用作数据分析，录像回放亦有助受训人员回顾整个训练，提升训练的质素。郭家俊高级警司指出 MR 训练系统中极高像真度的沉浸式体验，能令受训人员训练时更投入，为整个训练的效果大大提升。</p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">资料及图片来源：<a href="https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2005138/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E5%89%8D%E7%B7%9A%E9%83%A8%E9%9A%8A%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97-PTU%E5%BC%95%E5%85%A5-%E6%B7%B7%E5%90%88%E5%AF%A6%E5%A2%83-%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1-%E6%A8%A1%E6%93%AC%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%92%B0%E5%A2%83-%E5%8A%A9%E6%88%B0%E8%A1%93%E8%A8%93%E7%B7%B4%E7%B2%BE%E7%9B%8A%E6%B1%82%E7%B2%BE?fbclid=IwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTAAAR0swAB425v8LCzoXRJExakIBHvPfiSk7Z_bJzmHCDmR8G6VhTQYl_fqalo_aem_rysa03S-sLbDSPxB133l7g">星岛</a></span></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/12/htc-u24-pro/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">HTC 发布新手机 U24 Pro     支援 VIVE XR Elite VR 装置+ AI 拍照功能</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/18/lg-display-vr-oledos-10000nits/vr-mr-ar/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">LG Display VR 专属屏幕，高达 10,000nits 亮度</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/17/hkpolice-mr-training-system/fun-tech/">警队训练引入 Mixed Reality 技术，模拟不同环境供 PTU 作战术训练</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
